Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-lyrical-mrpt-libgui, ros-lyrical-mrpt-libmaps, ros-lyrical-mrpt-libnav, ros-lyrical-mrpt-libtclap, ros-lyrical-mvsim, ros-lyrical-ros-workspace
Description: Path planning and navigation algorithms for robots/vehicles moving on planar environments.
 This library builds upon mrpt-nav and the theory behind PTGs to generate libraries of "motion primitives" for vehicles with arbitrary shape and realistic kinematics and dynamics.
